articles.title: 3rd ODI: Ton-up Sanju Samson, Arshdeep Singh power India to 2-1 series win over South Africa - IndiaTimes
articles.description: Cricket News: Sanju Samson hit a fine century as India defeated South Africa by 78 runs in the third ODI to clinch the three-match series 2-1 in Paarl on Thursday.
